1
00:00:14,506 --> 00:00:19,944
<i>Connecting old words</i>
<i>that have been used up</i>

2
00:00:20,779 --> 00:00:28,686
<i>I just want to convey</i>
<i>my simple thoughts</i>

3
00:00:28,754 --> 00:00:34,124
<i>That day's faint wind blows away</i>

4
00:00:34,192 --> 00:00:38,253
<i>at the castle ruins of yesterday</i>

5
00:00:39,498 --> 00:00:44,401
<i>I'll laugh with you</i>
<i>and live for the moment</i>

6
00:00:45,137 --> 00:00:52,043
<i>Still that incident</i>
<i>will continue to trouble you, right?</i>

7
00:00:53,445 --> 00:00:56,937
<i>That's why it must be good bye</i>

8
00:00:57,015 --> 00:01:03,921
<i>Leaving nothing behind,</i>
<i>let us share what is left</i>

9
00:01:04,056 --> 00:01:11,121
<i>In time, we'll realize</i>
<i>that it was everything</i>

10
00:01:11,196 --> 00:01:17,863
<i>And sadness will touch our cheeks,</i>
<i>creating a river of tears</i>

11
00:01:18,270 --> 00:01:27,838
<i>Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex</i>
<i>and melting away</i>

12
00:01:31,293 --> 00:01:32,487
Yahoo!

13
00:01:32,561 --> 00:01:34,222
<i>Roar and Howl!</i>
<i>The Ultimate Tag Team!</i>

14
00:01:35,364 --> 00:01:36,331
<i>Got you!</i>

15
00:01:49,211 --> 00:01:50,109
Damn!

16
00:01:51,513 --> 00:01:52,639
<i>What's going on?!</i>

17
00:01:55,417 --> 00:01:57,851
<i>I felt a response to my attack,</i>
<i>but it didn't work.</i>

18
00:01:58,454 --> 00:02:00,319
<i>And where did his attack</i>
<i>come from?</i>

19
00:02:04,293 --> 00:02:05,385
Listen, Akamaru.

20
00:02:07,296 --> 00:02:09,457
We're gonna attack from both sides
with Fang Over Fang.

21
00:02:13,969 --> 00:02:14,560
Here we go!

22
00:02:19,341 --> 00:02:20,308
Fang Over Fang

23
00:02:22,578 --> 00:02:23,875
Summoning Jutsu!

24
00:02:34,490 --> 00:02:36,082
This doesn't look so good.

25
00:02:38,227 --> 00:02:40,491
I'll play a melody of death for you.

26
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:49,698
What's with this guy?

27
00:02:52,207 --> 00:02:52,730
<i>What?!</i>

28
00:02:55,711 --> 00:02:59,306
Two on two is perfect,
right, Sakon?

29
00:03:07,389 --> 00:03:10,290
How could the Sound Ninja Four
take so much time?

30
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:14,918
Did they send such strong people
after them who could hold them up...

31
00:03:15,631 --> 00:03:17,622
or are they playing around too much?

32
00:03:21,770 --> 00:03:24,432
Well, the one that's probably
delaying things is...

33
00:03:24,673 --> 00:03:29,440
either Jirobo who gets hungry a lot,
or Kidomaru who likes to play.

34
00:03:29,812 --> 00:03:31,677
But the one that's
the most dangerous

35
00:03:31,747 --> 00:03:33,408
when he loses his temper
is Sakon.

36
00:03:35,351 --> 00:03:37,842
He's not satisfied until
he kills his opponent,

37
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:39,881
even though he should
just leave things be.

38
00:03:40,656 --> 00:03:44,285
He thinks he's the strongest of
the four, so he shows off.

39
00:03:46,595 --> 00:03:47,789
I wonder if that's so...

40
00:03:48,497 --> 00:03:51,694
Tayuya has a personality that's
neck and neck with Sakon.

41
00:03:52,368 --> 00:03:54,598
But in any case,
nothing bad will happen

42
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:57,662
since we sent that kid...

43
00:03:59,575 --> 00:04:00,735
Kimimaro.

44
00:04:01,377 --> 00:04:08,180
He'll surely clean up anything that is
not good for me.

45
00:04:18,427 --> 00:04:20,861
I will never let you take Sasuke!

46
00:04:22,131 --> 00:04:24,599
There's a lot of trash scattered about.

47
00:04:26,535 --> 00:04:29,766
But after all, trash is trash.

48
00:04:30,472 --> 00:04:32,406
It simply needs to be cleaned up.

49
00:04:33,909 --> 00:04:35,206
Shut up!

50
00:04:38,247 --> 00:04:39,043
Come on.

51
00:04:40,382 --> 00:04:42,179
I'll crush you!

52
00:05:19,221 --> 00:05:21,451
<i>So this is the so called</i>
<i>melody of death.</i>

53
00:05:41,376 --> 00:05:42,809
<i>So she's manipulating them</i>
<i>with the sound of the flute.</i>

54
00:05:59,228 --> 00:06:02,857
<i>Damn! She's getting</i>
<i>further and further away.</i>

55
00:06:03,031 --> 00:06:05,591
<i>What should I do?!</i>
<i>What is it that I should do?!</i>

56
00:06:06,068 --> 00:06:06,693
<i>Huh?!</i>

57
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:09,861
<i>This is really looking bad!</i>

58
00:06:22,317 --> 00:06:23,284
Akamaru!

59
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,750
Oh, so you're the real one!

60
00:06:27,022 --> 00:06:27,886
Multiple Fists Barrage!

61
00:06:32,995 --> 00:06:34,121
One more!

62
00:06:40,602 --> 00:06:43,002
My brother and I get along very well.

63
00:06:43,605 --> 00:06:46,836
Usually, my older brother Ukon
sleeps inside of me,

64
00:06:46,942 --> 00:06:50,673
but when there's a fight
he comes out and helps out.

65
00:06:51,747 --> 00:06:53,908
<i>This is this guy's ability.</i>

66
00:06:54,149 --> 00:06:57,016
Ukon can stick out
his arms and legs, his head,

67
00:06:57,085 --> 00:07:00,577
from anywhere in my body
and attacks or defends.

68
00:07:00,789 --> 00:07:02,051
Like this you see...

69
00:07:06,528 --> 00:07:07,517
Multiple Legs Barrage!

70
00:07:13,435 --> 00:07:16,336
It's a three legged kick.
Works well, doesn't it?

71
00:07:16,638 --> 00:07:17,866
So next, it's...!

72
00:07:19,708 --> 00:07:22,871
There's no time to waste, Sakon.

73
00:07:28,283 --> 00:07:31,480
We'll finish this quickly!
Get into the second state!

74
00:07:35,023 --> 00:07:36,183
All right, all right...

75
00:07:41,563 --> 00:07:43,724
You're too impatient, bro.

76
00:07:50,906 --> 00:07:54,865
I see, you're saying those horns
aren't just for display, huh?

77
00:07:56,979 --> 00:07:59,174
<i>As soon as that right one came out,</i>

78
00:07:59,247 --> 00:08:01,613
<i>his Chakra increased</i>
<i>by several tenfold.</i>

79
00:08:02,517 --> 00:08:03,313
<i>Shoot!</i>

80
00:08:03,885 --> 00:08:06,979
<i>It seemed hopeless before,</i>
<i>but now it's really bad.</i>

81
00:08:10,592 --> 00:08:12,389
What's your liking, bro?

82
00:08:13,562 --> 00:08:14,756
In pieces.

83
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:46,720
So now,
perhaps it's time to get serious.

84
00:08:47,864 --> 00:08:49,525
I'll take care of you all at once.

85
00:08:50,767 --> 00:08:55,067
Such confident words!
But those are <i>my</i> lines!

86
00:09:02,145 --> 00:09:04,636
<i>Shoot! These guys are persistent!</i>

87
00:09:05,248 --> 00:09:08,376
<i>But it's starting to</i>
<i>get clearer to me.</i>

88
00:09:14,591 --> 00:09:17,458
<i>But the problem is</i>
<i>from here on out.</i>

89
00:09:22,131 --> 00:09:24,895
<i>Damn! Am I completely out of hands?</i>

90
00:09:27,704 --> 00:09:30,434
What?! You're saying
we're gonna do that?!

91
00:09:31,975 --> 00:09:33,101
No, Akamaru!

92
00:09:33,843 --> 00:09:36,437
It's too dangerous to do it here
without our comrades!

93
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,338
You understand, don't you?

94
00:09:39,048 --> 00:09:40,606
If we use that Jutsu,

95
00:09:40,683 --> 00:09:42,947
both you and I will use up
most of our Chakra

96
00:09:43,019 --> 00:09:44,486
and won't be able to move.

97
00:09:45,622 --> 00:09:48,614
If we miss, we'll die here in vain.

98
00:09:54,097 --> 00:09:55,064
Akamaru...

99
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:07,933
<i>What a pitiful master I am...</i>
<i>that you had to bite me.</i>

100
00:10:09,913 --> 00:10:11,175
<i>I understand, Akamaru.</i>

101
00:10:11,814 --> 00:10:14,442
<i>Just like you said,</i>
<i>we only have that left!</i>

102
00:10:16,586 --> 00:10:17,518
Wolf Fang Over Fang!

103
00:10:31,935 --> 00:10:32,959
Now, Akamaru!

104
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:34,461
<i>What?!</i>

105
00:10:36,306 --> 00:10:38,171
<i>Do it well...Akamaru!</i>

106
00:10:38,608 --> 00:10:40,405
<i>Show them the results of the training!</i>

107
00:10:45,348 --> 00:10:46,940
<i>It's Dynamic Marking!</i>

108
00:10:48,284 --> 00:10:50,184
Playing dirty like that!

109
00:10:51,187 --> 00:10:52,654
<i>All preparations are done!</i>

110
00:10:54,924 --> 00:10:57,017
<i>Inuzuka Style!</i>
<i>Man Beast Transformation Combo!</i>

111
00:11:07,937 --> 00:11:09,063
<i>Two Headed Wolf!</i>

112
00:11:19,449 --> 00:11:20,780
I wondered what it was going
to be and

113
00:11:20,850 --> 00:11:23,045
it turned out to be
a drooling runt of a dog.

114
00:11:23,386 --> 00:11:25,354
What can a dog like this do?

115
00:11:28,691 --> 00:11:29,316
Take this!

116
00:11:34,497 --> 00:11:35,429
<i>Drool?!</i>

117
00:11:35,565 --> 00:11:37,328
Sakon, what're you doing!
To the right!

118
00:11:37,834 --> 00:11:38,459
Damn!

119
00:11:39,202 --> 00:11:40,362
Wolf Fang Over Fang!

120
00:12:00,590 --> 00:12:02,023
<i>Heh! How's that!</i>

121
00:12:02,625 --> 00:12:04,957
<i>Wolf Fang Over Fang revolution speed</i>
<i>is too fast.</i>

122
00:12:05,128 --> 00:12:09,155
<i>It's such an intense high revolution that</i>
<i>even our visibility becomes zero.</i>

123
00:12:09,499 --> 00:12:11,797
<i>Even without direct contact,</i>
<i>flesh is cut...</i>

124
00:12:11,934 --> 00:12:13,868
<i>A direct hit from the blow</i>
<i>and you're in pieces.</i>

125
00:12:37,994 --> 00:12:41,191
Really... getting carried away...

126
00:12:41,831 --> 00:12:46,029
This is perfect.
We were just thinking of separating soon.

127
00:12:46,335 --> 00:12:49,065
What?! He divided into two people?!

128
00:12:49,572 --> 00:12:50,300
It's true...

129
00:12:52,575 --> 00:12:55,635
Had we fully received the blow as one,
it would've been bad, but...

130
00:12:55,778 --> 00:12:57,746
The real battle begins now.

131
00:12:59,082 --> 00:13:00,379
Damn it...

132
00:13:03,052 --> 00:13:05,885
Yeah... I know Akamaru.

133
00:13:06,689 --> 00:13:08,281
One more shot of
Wolf Fang Over Fang.

134
00:13:08,958 --> 00:13:10,482
The next one is our limit.

135
00:13:13,429 --> 00:13:14,657
We'll take them down with this!

136
00:13:15,765 --> 00:13:16,663
Wolf Fang Over Fang!

137
00:13:22,972 --> 00:13:24,200
It's no use hiding!

138
00:13:24,707 --> 00:13:26,868
I told you we don't chase
with our eyes!

139
00:13:27,610 --> 00:13:31,478
We attack by chasing smells
we've marked with our noses!

140
00:13:39,355 --> 00:13:40,720
- A!
- Un!

141
00:13:41,324 --> 00:13:42,256
- Summoning...
- Summoning...

142
00:13:43,793 --> 00:13:44,919
- Rashomon!
- Rashomon!

143
00:13:59,408 --> 00:14:01,376
<i>That's an impressive power...</i>

144
00:14:01,444 --> 00:14:03,241
<i>To turn Rashomon,</i>

145
00:14:03,312 --> 00:14:07,146
<i>the ultimate shield to protect</i>
<i>Lord Orochimaru into this shape.</i>

146
00:14:07,517 --> 00:14:08,449
<i>But...</i>

147
00:14:14,757 --> 00:14:16,054
- This is the end!
- This is the end!

148
00:14:24,567 --> 00:14:25,556
Akamaru!

149
00:14:26,002 --> 00:14:29,233
<i>Akamaru...</i>
<i>To protect me, you...</i>

150
00:14:30,239 --> 00:14:32,764
Damn! He did it again!

151
00:14:33,743 --> 00:14:34,573
My eyes...!

152
00:14:35,378 --> 00:14:36,538
<i>Damn!</i>

153
00:14:37,013 --> 00:14:40,414
Damn...!
This time it's not ordinary piss!

154
00:14:40,917 --> 00:14:43,818
It feels like my eyes are burning
with strong acid!

155
00:14:45,454 --> 00:14:46,751
<i>Where's the other one?!</i>

156
00:14:47,623 --> 00:14:48,555
Hey...

157
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:52,252
Who are you looking for?

158
00:14:54,897 --> 00:14:58,697
I'll take care of the rest.
Go wash your eyes in that river.

159
00:15:03,105 --> 00:15:07,007
This is my ability...
specialized in assassination, of course.

160
00:15:07,376 --> 00:15:12,075
You can't beat me by
just having a good nose and nails.

161
00:15:12,682 --> 00:15:14,912
You can't beat my ability!

162
00:15:17,687 --> 00:15:19,985
You know that the Chakra Network
through which Chakra flows

163
00:15:20,056 --> 00:15:23,787
is deeply interwoven with each
internal organ, right?

164
00:15:24,794 --> 00:15:29,254
The Chakra Network is interwoven
in a variety of complicated ways

165
00:15:29,332 --> 00:15:32,790
and is linked to the tissues that
make up each organ.

166
00:15:33,236 --> 00:15:35,397
A Iso to each cell that makes up
the tissues,

167
00:15:35,471 --> 00:15:39,999
as well as even to proteins,
which are the main component of cells...

168
00:15:40,676 --> 00:15:42,143
At the second state,

169
00:15:42,211 --> 00:15:47,581
I can dismantle or reconstruct these cells
or proteins as I wish by using Chakra.

170
00:15:48,985 --> 00:15:50,475
To put it simply,

171
00:15:50,553 --> 00:15:53,886
I can turn my body into tiny pieces,
enter my opponent's body...

172
00:15:53,956 --> 00:15:57,357
return to my original form
and come back out.

173
00:15:57,994 --> 00:15:59,154
<i>Akamaru...</i>

174
00:16:00,229 --> 00:16:02,129
<i>I'm sorry... Akamaru...!</i>

175
00:16:03,299 --> 00:16:05,324
<i>We've always done things together...</i>

176
00:16:05,768 --> 00:16:07,668
<i>we were together,</i>
<i>always and everywhere.</i>

177
00:16:15,678 --> 00:16:18,340
Yahoo! Good boy, Akamaru!

178
00:16:19,215 --> 00:16:24,812
Yahoo! We're lucky that the people
who got into our trap had Earth Scroll!

179
00:16:25,388 --> 00:16:28,118
With our luck like this,
we'll reach the goal first.

180
00:16:37,066 --> 00:16:38,897
Akamaru is frightened
all of a sudden.

181
00:16:39,635 --> 00:16:44,095
He can smell the strength of
an oppoenent's Chakra.

182
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:47,302
I've never seen him this scared...

183
00:16:48,311 --> 00:16:52,304
The people fighting over there must
be something...

184
00:16:52,815 --> 00:16:57,377
The Seventh Round Battle.
Naruto Uzumaki vs. Kiba Inuzuka.

185
00:16:58,454 --> 00:17:00,945
Hey! First of all, don't you bring
a puppy in here!

186
00:17:01,023 --> 00:17:02,547
He'll get in the way of our battle!

187
00:17:02,625 --> 00:17:05,651
Idiot! Akamaru is fighting along with me!

188
00:17:07,163 --> 00:17:07,925
Now then...

189
00:17:09,432 --> 00:17:10,660
Let's go, Akamaru!

190
00:17:13,602 --> 00:17:14,432
Eat this!

191
00:17:29,051 --> 00:17:29,847
There!

192
00:17:31,988 --> 00:17:36,516
Naruto... I'm taking Akamaru back.

193
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:56,603
Wh-What?! What did you feed him?
His coating has changed to red!

194
00:17:56,779 --> 00:17:59,441
That's why his name is Akamaru.

195
00:18:00,383 --> 00:18:01,782
Let's go, Akamaru!

196
00:18:03,986 --> 00:18:05,783
Beast Mimicry Ninja Art:

197
00:18:13,796 --> 00:18:15,127
Man Beast Clone!

198
00:18:16,866 --> 00:18:19,130
Let's go! All-Four...

199
00:18:19,802 --> 00:18:21,497
Jutsu!

200
00:18:43,259 --> 00:18:44,123
An opening!

201
00:18:45,327 --> 00:18:47,795
Take this!
Man Beast Ultimate Taijutsu!

202
00:18:51,367 --> 00:18:52,891
Fang Over Fang

203
00:19:15,958 --> 00:19:16,754
Akamaru!

204
00:19:19,261 --> 00:19:20,319
Here, Food Pills.

205
00:19:31,173 --> 00:19:33,334
Akamaru! Human Mimicry Ninja Art!

206
00:19:51,460 --> 00:19:52,427
Fang Over Fang

207
00:19:59,502 --> 00:20:03,461
<i>However, this one time,</i>
<i>I'm sunk...</i>

208
00:20:04,206 --> 00:20:09,007
My cells can swim inside
your body as I wish,

209
00:20:09,078 --> 00:20:11,774
and I can even create parts
that are only you.

210
00:20:11,847 --> 00:20:14,577
In other words,
a little bit of a fusion condition.

211
00:20:14,817 --> 00:20:17,217
A sharing of the flesh is what it'll be.

212
00:20:18,220 --> 00:20:19,983
A sharing?

213
00:20:20,756 --> 00:20:25,455
That's right... and a cruel way
of killing that only I can accomplish...

214
00:20:26,228 --> 00:20:29,994
The gradual scraping away
of just <i>your</i> cells.

215
00:20:30,566 --> 00:20:31,590
I see.

216
00:20:39,508 --> 00:20:40,475
If that's the case...!

217
00:20:50,186 --> 00:20:53,883
If I do this, what's gonna happen?

218
00:20:55,791 --> 00:20:58,919
Suicide?! That's ridiculous!

219
00:21:01,330 --> 00:21:03,264
Die with me...

220
00:21:11,309 --> 00:21:13,709
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

221
00:21:13,778 --> 00:21:16,804
<i>And you smiled</i>

222
00:21:17,048 --> 00:21:19,346
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

223
00:21:19,417 --> 00:21:22,147
<i>In my own words</i>

224
00:21:22,220 --> 00:21:27,783
<i>Would you think it was</i>
<i>a bother if I approached you?</i>

225
00:21:28,126 --> 00:21:33,325
<i>Despite my doubts,</i>
<i>I worked up my courage</i>

226
00:21:33,598 --> 00:21:39,002
<i>My clumsy attempts with words</i>

227
00:21:39,204 --> 00:21:44,733
<i>You listened without turning away</i>

228
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:50,909
<i>No wonder I get carried away by you</i>

229
00:21:51,316 --> 00:21:57,983
<i>But you don't feel anything for me, do you?</i>

230
00:21:58,490 --> 00:22:01,186
<i>I feel so sad</i>

231
00:22:01,259 --> 00:22:02,157
<i>But...</i>

232
00:22:02,227 --> 00:22:04,627
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

233
00:22:04,696 --> 00:22:07,665
<i>And you smiled</i>

234
00:22:07,799 --> 00:22:10,393
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

235
00:22:10,468 --> 00:22:13,460
<i>In my own words</i>

236
00:22:13,638 --> 00:22:15,970
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

237
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:19,168
<i>And you smiled</i>

238
00:22:19,244 --> 00:22:21,712
<i>For the first time, I was able to speak</i>

239
00:22:21,780 --> 00:22:24,681
<i>In my own words</i>

240
00:22:24,883 --> 00:22:29,320
<i>For the first time, I spoke to you</i>

241
00:22:37,729 --> 00:22:41,062
What is this guy?
Kekkei Genkai?!

242
00:22:41,733 --> 00:22:45,601
Damn it! I've never heard
or seen this kind of technique!

243
00:22:46,004 --> 00:22:48,404
Despite the fact that
this many are attacking him,

244
00:22:48,473 --> 00:22:50,532
my attacks don't even faze him!

245
00:22:51,943 --> 00:22:54,571
I don't know if it's
the "Five Dances" or what,

246
00:22:54,979 --> 00:22:58,574
but I'll take care of them all!

247
00:22:59,751 --> 00:23:02,311
Next time: "To Each His Own Battle"
